# SEO site verification — do not remove

Google Search Console and Naver Search Advisor ownership depend on meta tags injected on the homepage (`/` and `/index.html`).

## Protected locations

| File | What to keep |
|------|----------------|
| `server/main.py` | `GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION`, `NAVER_SITE_VERIFICATION` env defaults + `_home_html()` / `serve_home()` |
| `server/seo.py` | `inject_home_seo()` must emit both `<meta name="google-site-verification">` and `<meta name="naver-site-verification">` |
| `render.yaml` | Both env var keys and values for production |

## Current verification values (change only when re-verifying in consoles)

